  - Keeper
  - Keeper
  - Keeper
  - Keeper
  - Keeper
  dialogue:
  - Pick up the rod and look for what you want to catch.
  - Hold [Left Mouse Button] to begin aiming your bobber.
  - Once you're set, let it go to throw out the line. But be careful not to directly
    hit the fish or you'll scare them off.
  - With the bobber out in the water, nearby fish will be attracted to it.
  - When a fish bites, click [Left Mouse Button] at just the right time to reel it
    in.
  - Once you've caught one it'll go in that barrel there. You can check how much
    you've caught by interacting with the scale [E].
  - Also be sure to be wary of your time out here. You'll only want to spend so much
    time amongst the waves.
  - So check the clock fer how much time you have [E].
